<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV93">
<l>kālaivey yōṟkumuṉ ṉōṭṭuk koṭuttakaṅ kuṟkuṟumpar</l>
<l>mālaivey yōṉpaṭa vaiyakam pāvuva raṉṉakaṇṭuṅ</l>
<l>kālainaṉ ñāṉat tuṟaipaṭin tāṭikkaṇ pōtuceytu</l>
<l>mālainaṉ ṉāviṟkoḷ ḷārniṉai yāravaṉ maippaṭiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though thus seeing those whose stronghold is the night, who give flight</l>
<l>before the hot [sun] by morning, spread over the world when the hot [sun] sets by evening,</l>
<l>they won’t settle [and] bathe in the ford of good knowledge in the morning,</l>
<l>[their] eyes budding [tears, and] take garlands on [their] good tongues, they won’t think of his kajal body.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
